    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I am pleased that Gov. Christine Todd Whitman of New Jersey says she will ask the appropriate members of her cabinet to ''reassess everything that we have done'' to prevent the West Nile virus (news article, Sept. 28). I would like to hear from Mayor Rudolph W. Giuliani that he plans to do the same and that he will address the public on certain critical questions.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>I am pleased that Gov. Christine Todd Whitman of New Jersey says she will ask the appropriate members of her cabinet to ''reassess everything that we have done'' to prevent the West Nile virus (news article, Sept. 28). I would like to hear from Mayor Rudolph W. Giuliani that he plans to do the same and that he will address the public on certain critical questions.</p>
        <p>What has the effect of the spraying been on the people of the city? What has the effect of the spraying been on the rest of the ecosystem? What will be the long-term effect of continued spraying?</p>
        <p>PETER RHOADES MOTT  Bronx, Sept. 28, 2000</p>
      </block>
